Package document

Interface TextDocument

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    TextDocumentImpl
    public interface TextDocument
    This interface represents all the operations offered by a text document. The text document can count its words and can compare two documents for similarity.

    • Method Summary

      All Methods Instance Methods Abstract Methods 
      Modifier and Type Method Description
      java.lang.String getText()
      Return the contents of this document.
      int getWordCount()
      Return the number of words in this document.
      java.lang.String minusDiff​(TextDocument other)
      Computes the subsequence of characters that need to be removed from this document such that the remainder is a subsequence in the other document.
      java.lang.String plusDiff​(TextDocument other)
      Computes the subsequence of characters in other that needs to be added to this document after removing the characters obtained from minusDiff(TextDocument).
